reviewText: The tab booklet is included as a PDF file on the dvd. This is an excellent instructional video that carefully walks you through some classic fingerpicking tunes. Miller offers helpful pointers on tough spots. By the way, I'm no relation. Just love the songs and the teaching.
This DVD is mailed out without the "FREE" tab/music booklet that is stated on the cover of the DVD case.

I've become entranced with the rag time songs of Elizabeth Cotton.  This is one video that really walks the relative novice (me) thru the songs.  I've been able to incrementally learn some classics.  And the videos of Elizabeth playing her songs, as no other can,  all I can say is "wow!"
